    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your<strong> leek[s] </strong>in half lengthways, wash thoroughly to remove any grit then top, tail and slice finely</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 500ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
