            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter </strong>over a medium heat</p><p>Add your <strong>orzo</strong>, <strong>sliced leek</strong> and <strong>chopped garlic</strong> with a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the orzo in butter</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
