        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the orzo is cooking, chop your <strong>dill </strong>finely, including the stalks</p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Season your <strong>salmon fillet[s] </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
