    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>prasorizo-style dill orzo</strong> topped with the <strong>oregano salmon </strong>and the<strong> salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the<strong> toasted pine nuts </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and a small drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
